text: Karl-Heinz Munk (born 11 December 1939) is a German ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the United Team of Germany Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Hallenberg
